* Syntax: {{CodeSelect|code=
{{ExtLink
{{!}}text=Kicksecure Homepage
{{!}}https://www.kicksecure.com
{{!}}https://web.archive.org/web/https://www.kicksecure.com
{{!}}http://www.w5j6stm77zs6652pgsij4awcjeel3eco7kvipheu6mtr623eyyehj4yd.onion
}}
}}
* Result: {{ExtLink
|text=Kicksecure Homepage
|https://www.kicksecure.com
|https://web.archive.org/web/https://www.kicksecure.com
|http://www.w5j6stm77zs6652pgsij4awcjeel3eco7kvipheu6mtr623eyyehj4yd.onion
